                         SES v4.1 file for testing the reading and conversion of forms.
                         Handles most forms - only ones missing are 6H (weird, causes a crash),
                         4A (this is an aero/thermo run not a fire run), 8E (explicit train speed) and
                         10 (stationary trains).

                         Humidity displayed as relative humidity
                         Print option set to zero (designer oriented output)
